ITTEL_1" data-partID="k1"><h2>I</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1">Med hjemmel i § 1 i lov av 3. juni 1938 nr. 3 om smittsomme sykdommer på bier blir fastsatt at sykdommene:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="1)" data-name="1)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1"><span class="data-originalId">1)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/1/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">Kalkyngel (Ascosphaera apis)</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="2)" data-name="2)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/2/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-2"><span class="data-originalId">2)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">Yngelmidd (Varroa jocobsoni) og</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="3)" data-name="3)"><article class="listArticle" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/3/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-3"><span class="data-originalId">3)</span><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/1/ledd/1/punkt/3/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-1-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">Trakémidd (Acarapis woodi) skal gå inn under loven.</article></article></li></ul></article></section><section class="section" data-name="kapII" data-section-type="default" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/" id="kapittel-2" data-lovdata-URL="LTI/forskrift/1985-01-25-159/KAPITTEL_2" data-partID="k2"><h2>II</h2><article class="legalP" data-absoluteaddress="/kapittel/2/ledd/1/" id="kapittel-2-ledd-1">Denne resolusjon trer i kraft straks.</article></section></main></body></html>